24/02/2008
ZAGREB, Croatia -- Police announced on Saturday (February 23rd) they busted a drug trafficking channel seizing about 13kg of cocaine worth around 550,000 euros and arresting 10 people. 
Croatian authorities continue to look for a 53-year-old Croat with Croatian and Dutch citizenship, who is the alleged organiser of the drug trafficking channel from South America through Africa to the Dutch and Belgian ports and then to Croatia. 
(Hina, HRT, AFP - 23/02/08)
